Dialogue: 100,0:00:08.40,0:00:11.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}天气不错啊 是吧?\N{\rENG}Lovely day, isn't it? 
Dialogue: 600,0:00:08.40,0:00:11.37,Hint,,0,0,0,,史蒂文的秃顶源自著名心理学博士Steven C. Hayes
Dialogue: 100,0:00:11.40,0:00:14.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还行吧\N{\rENG}Yeah, I guess. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:15.94,0:00:17.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你造 我爸爸告诉过我\N{\rENG}Ya know, uh, my dad told me
Dialogue: 100,0:00:17.74,0:00:19.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}到了一定岁数这种事就会发生的\N{\rENG}I should probably expect this at some point, 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:19.55,0:00:21.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我也没想到会是一夜之间那么快\N{\rENG}but I didn't think it would happen overnight. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:21.58,0:00:22.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对啊 不错\N{\rENG}Right, yeah. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:27.62,0:00:29.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮! 我秃了!\N{\rENG}Connie, I'm bald! 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:29.79,0:00:32.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 发生了什么事?\N{\rENG}Oh. What happened? 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.73,0:00:35.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没事 只是个笑话而已\N{\rENG}Nothing. It was just a joke. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.06,0:00:37.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 好吧\N{\rENG}Oh, okay. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.56,0:00:39.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 你还好吗?\N{\rENG}Hey, are you okay? 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.42,0:00:43.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 康妮!\N{\rENG}Steven, Connie! 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:43.11,0:00:45.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}希望你们准备好学习今天的特殊课程了\N{\rENG}I hope you two are ready for today's special lesson. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:46.01,0:00:48.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 不 我是不是应该带什么东西来着?\N{\rENG}Oh, no, was I supposed to bring something? 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.41,0:00:49.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}带上自己就好\N{\rENG}Just yourselves. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.74,0:00:51.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴会参与旁听\N{\rENG}Garnet is going to sit in. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.18,0:00:54.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}能看你俩作为史蒂翁妮战斗她非常激动\N{\rENG}She's very excited to see you fight as Stevonnie. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.81,0:00:56.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦! 对啊!\N{\rENG}Oh! Right! 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.65,0:00:57.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}融合训练\N{\rENG}Fusion training. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.88,0:01:00.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我做了个口号板\N{\rENG}I made a sign. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:00.52,0:01:01.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这面是为你们俩加油\N{\rENG}This side is for both of you. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:01.99,0:01:03.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这面是为史蒂翁妮加油\N{\rENG}And this sideis for Stevonnie. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.02,0:01:05.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一体两面的\N{\rENG}It's two signs in one. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:05.63,0:01:07.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}融合口号\N{\rENG}A fusion sign. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:07.43,0:01:09.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}融合笑话!\N{\rENG}Fusion joke! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:12.10,0:01:13.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}准备好了吗?\N{\rENG}Ready, kids? 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.57,0:01:14.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好了 老师\N{\rENG}Yes, ma'am! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:15.00,0:01:16.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}-康妮!-好了 老师!\N{\rENG}-Connie!-Yes, ma'am! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:16.87,0:01:19.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文! 康妮! 喔!\N{\rENG}Ste-ven! Con-nie! Whoo! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:19.84,0:01:22.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}启动融合舞蹈\N{\rENG}Initiating fusion dance. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:24.04,0:01:26.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}来打我啊 孩子们\N{\rENG}Come at me, children. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:36.32,0:01:39.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不如跳舞\N{\rENG}Let's dance. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.59,0:01:43.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}准备...开始!\N{\rENG}Let us...begin! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:53.34,0:01:54.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哈?\N{\rENG}Huh? 
Dialogue: 600,0:01:51.04,0:01:52.05,Hint,,0,0,0,,史蒂翁妮的动作出自"超级马里奥兄弟"
Dialogue: 100,0:01:55.54,0:01:57.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦!\N{\rENG}Oh! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:58.29,0:01:59.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好棒!\N{\rENG}All right! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:59.61,0:02:01.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂翁妮有悬浮能力了!\N{\rENG}Stevonnie's got floating powers! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:01.75,0:02:03.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是时候干掉你了!\N{\rENG}Time to finish the job! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哈? 我很抱歉!\N{\rENG}Huh? I'm sorry! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文! 康妮!\N{\rENG}Steven! Connie! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:14.69,0:02:15.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}发-发生啥事?\N{\rENG}W-What happened? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:16.03,0:02:17.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯啊!\N{\rENG}Mmmuh! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:18.47,0:02:20.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮 等下!\N{\rENG}Connie, wait! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:28.07,0:02:30.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 你怎么了?\N{\rENG}Hey, what's wrong? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:30.48,0:02:32.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我在学校做了很糟糕的事\N{\rENG}I did something terrible at school, 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:32.78,0:02:34.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在不知道该怎么办\N{\rENG}and I don't know what to do. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:34.71,0:02:36.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘛 听起来不像你的风格\N{\rENG}Well, that doesn't sound like you. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:36.78,0:02:37.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}发生了什么?\N{\rENG}What happened? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.59,0:02:40.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我打了一个同学\N{\rENG}I beat someone up. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:40.99,0:02:41.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啥?\N{\rENG}What? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:41.99,0:02:43.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一个不认识的小孩\N{\rENG}A kid I didn't know. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.72,0:02:45.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他在走廊上撞到了我\N{\rENG}He just bumped into me in the hallway. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:45.93,0:02:48.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我吓了一跳 然后战斗本能被激发了\N{\rENG}I was so startled, my training instincts kicked in. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:48.93,0:02:50.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我反击了\N{\rENG}I just reacted. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:50.83,0:02:53.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我觉得太丢人了 就跑掉了\N{\rENG}I was so embarrassed, I just ran away. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:54.00,0:02:55.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是你不是有意伤害他的!\N{\rENG}But you didn't mean to hurt him! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:55.77,0:02:58.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道那种感觉\N{\rENG}I know what it's like. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.04,0:03:01.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有时候 你会不小心伤害到别人\N{\rENG}Sometimes, you hurt people by accident. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:01.77,0:03:04.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你-你不去想它就好了\N{\rENG}Y-you just have to try not to think about it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.74,0:03:07.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}先别说话\N{\rENG}Hold the phone. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:07.05,0:03:09.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}交给我来说\N{\rENG}Now give the phone to me. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.42,0:03:14.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}融合能正常存在 取决于平衡\N{\rENG}For a fusion to work, there needs to be balance. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:14.09,0:03:16.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不平衡会导致你的融合\N{\rENG}An imbalancecan cause your fusion
Dialogue: 100,0:03:16.06,0:03:17.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}失去对现实的把握\N{\rENG}to lose touch with reality, 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:17.72,0:03:20.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}产生各种幻觉 最终破碎解体\N{\rENG}see things that aren't there, and eventually fall apart. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:20.93,0:03:24.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也就是说 你俩其中一个迷失的话 \N{\rENG}That is to say, if one of you is falling apart, 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.10,0:03:26.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们的融合也会解体\N{\rENG}your fusion will as well. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:26.43,0:03:29.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为了找到平衡 你们必须了解自己的情感\N{\rENG}To find balance, you must understand your feelings. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:29.64,0:03:32.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为了了解自己的情感 你们需要透彻地看待它们\N{\rENG}To understand your feelings, you must see them clearly
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.51,0:03:34.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而不是逃避它们\N{\rENG}without running from them. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:34.44,0:03:36.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}透彻地看?\N{\rENG}See them clearly? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:36.04,0:03:39.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我会展示的 不过首先 我们需要史蒂翁妮来\N{\rENG}I'll show you, but first, we'll need Stevonnie. 
