Dialogue: 100,0:03:52.39,0:03:54.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好的\N{\rENG}Okay. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:54.76,0:03:55.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}深呼吸\N{\rENG}Breathe. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.70,0:04:03.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在这儿 在黑暗中 一切安好\N{\rENG}Here, in darkness, everything's okay. 
