Dialogue: 100,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 我准备好训练了!\N{\rENG}Steven, I'm ready to train! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我很高兴和石榴谈话了\N{\rENG}I'm so glad we talked to Garnet. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.82,0:07:38.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我想到该怎么做了!\N{\rENG}I really figured outwhat I needed to do! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:38.65,0:07:39.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我和杰夫谈过了!\N{\rENG}I talked to Jeff! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:39.82,0:07:41.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他叫杰夫 顺便说一下\N{\rENG}That's his name, by the way. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:41.25,0:07:43.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哇 你做到了\N{\rENG}Whoa, you did it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:43.26,0:07:46.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我道歉了 他也理解我了\N{\rENG}I apologizedand he understood! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:46.03,0:07:48.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他事实上还想让我给他表演几招\N{\rENG}He actually wanted to know if I could show him some moves. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.69,0:07:50.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}-很不错啊\N{\rENG}-That's great! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:50.53,0:07:51.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}想来真有趣\N{\rENG}It's funny. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我花了那么多时间沉浸在不安中\N{\rENG}I spent all that time feeling bad
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}却没有采取任何行动\N{\rENG}instead of doing something. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:56.00,0:07:58.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好像我越是试着不去想它\N{\rENG}It's like I was trying not to think about it, 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.27,0:08:00.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}事情就变得越糟\N{\rENG}and that just made it worse. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.14,0:08:01.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在我思绪清晰了 \N{\rENG}Now that I've got a clear head, 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.67,0:08:04.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们作为史蒂翁妮会表现出色的\N{\rENG}we'll do so much better as Stevonnie. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.04,0:08:05.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不说了 我得换衣服了!\N{\rENG}Anyway, I'm gonna change! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.12,0:08:19.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}很棒的技巧 史蒂翁妮\N{\rENG}Great technique, Stevonnie. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}继续保持!\N{\rENG}Keep it up! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢夸奖 老师!\N{\rENG}Thanks, ma'am! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.13,0:08:24.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗨呀!\N{\rENG}Hyah! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.26,0:08:25.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 啊...\N{\rENG}Uh, uh...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 哦 啊...\N{\rENG}Oh, oh, uh...
Dialogue: 600,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.10,Hint,,0,0,0,,这里的黄色调源自"脐轮"与"降世神通"相同
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 不\N{\rENG}Oh, no. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.60,0:08:33.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}又开始了!\N{\rENG}It's happening again! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她是谁啊?\N{\rENG}Who was that? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.94,0:08:38.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是铋斯姆--史蒂文--哦 不\N{\rENG}Bismuth--Steven--oh, no. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:38.21,0:08:40.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这次是我的问题了!\N{\rENG}It's coming from me now! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:40.28,0:08:41.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}-史蒂翁妮!-啊\N{\rENG}-Stevonnie!-U-uh! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.91,0:08:43.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}深呼吸!\N{\rENG}Breathe! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.15,0:08:44.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}发生了什么?\N{\rENG}What's going on? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.25,0:08:45.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他们怎么了?\N{\rENG}What's happening to them? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.82,0:08:46.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他们能做到的!\N{\rENG}They've got this! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:46.89,0:08:50.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对 我-我能-呃\N{\rENG}Y-yeah, I'm...I'm...ugh. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:52.02,0:08:54.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}铁石英\N{\rENG}Jasper. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:54.93,0:08:57.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我-我试着帮你来的\N{\rENG}I-I tried to help you. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.10,0:08:58.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是你选择不听的\N{\rENG}You wouldn't listen. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:58.70,0:09:01.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我-我说过让你停下!\N{\rENG}I--I told you to stop! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我-我也别无选择!\N{\rENG}I-I had no choice! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:03.10,0:09:05.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我-我很抱歉! 我不该--\N{\rENG}I-I'm sorry. I shouldn't be--
Dialogue: 100,0:09:05.07,0:09:07.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不! 没关系的!\N{\rENG}No! It's okay! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:07.27,0:09:09.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}想这些事没关系的!\N{\rENG}It's okay to think about it! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.21,0:09:12.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我以为没关系的 但是我承受不住!\N{\rENG}I thought I could, but it's so much! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:12.18,0:09:14.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我做不到!\N{\rENG}I can't do it! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊!\N{\rENG}Ahh! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:17.85,0:09:19.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊!\N{\rENG}Ah! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:25.22,0:09:27.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不\N{\rENG}No. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不\N{\rENG}No. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.89,0:09:31.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不\N{\rENG}No. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.56,0:09:32.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂翁妮!\N{\rENG}Stevonnie! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.13,0:09:36.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们在坠落!\N{\rENG}We're falling! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 和我融合!\N{\rENG}Steven, let's fuse! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们能悬浮的 我们会没事的!\N{\rENG}We can hover. We'll be okay! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:41.21,0:09:42.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文?\N{\rENG}Steven? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.71,0:09:44.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我没有想伤害任何人!\N{\rENG}I didn't want to hurt anyone! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.94,0:09:47.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我很抱歉!\N{\rENG}I'm sorry! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:47.25,0:09:48.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们没有一个接受我的帮助!\N{\rENG}None of them would let me help them! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:48.85,0:09:49.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我也别无选择!\N{\rENG}I had no choice! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:49.92,0:09:51.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没关系的!\N{\rENG}It's okay! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:51.28,0:09:53.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不! 有关系!\N{\rENG}No, it's not! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:53.09,0:09:54.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但你回想这些事是可以的!\N{\rENG}But it's okay to think about it! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.79,0:09:56.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}感觉太难受了\N{\rENG}It feels so bad. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:56.76,0:09:58.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那也没关系!\N{\rENG}That's okay, too! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:58.19,0:10:00.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当时你也没有其他的选择!\N{\rENG}There was nothing else you could have done! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.66,0:10:02.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不想感觉这么糟\N{\rENG}I don't want to feel this way. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.53,0:10:03.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不得不\N{\rENG}You have to. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.96,0:10:06.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你需要正面对待这些糟糕的情感\N{\rENG}You have to be honest about how bad it feels
Dialogue: 100,0:10:06.60,0:10:07.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这样才能跨过去\N{\rENG}so you can move on. 
Dialogue: 600,0:10:04.60,0:10:06.60,Hint,,0,0,0,,像不像"千与千寻"? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.93,0:10:09.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我就是这么做的\N{\rENG}That's how it was for me. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:12.14,0:10:13.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧\N{\rENG}Okay. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.98,0:10:23.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}深呼吸就好\N{\rENG}Just breathe. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:34.99,0:10:37.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯-\N{\rENG}Mm-mm-mm. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:44.70,0:10:47.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我在这里\N{\rENG}I'm here. 

